Project Description
Simple 3D demo of my WPF Chomium WebBrowser control.

You'll also need AwesomiumWrapper and Cjc.ChromiumBrowser source from the associated WPF Chromium WebBrowser project: http://wpfchromium.codeplex.com/SourceControl/ListDownloadableCommits.aspx (http://wpfchromium.codeplex.com).

For details, see related post: http://chriscavanagh.wordpress.com/2009/08/27/wpf-3d-chromium-browser/
